          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "于矫激，或者大圣大贤，能造寡欲养心之绝诣，庶几出此藩篱。然当今之世，孰为圣，孰为贤，实未之见闻，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "亦无怪乎剧本中之花大汉也。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "根据《戏考》第十七册整理"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王氏上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王氏 （小调转五更） 怕到黄昏，怕到黄昏，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "黄昏已定，起了初更。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "手挽乌云，手挽乌云。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "撞罢钟，就把更来定。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人生最苦是别离，难舍难分没了期。相逢相见知何日，死别生离两处飞。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴家王氏。丈夫花大汉，在营中吃了一分口粮，明日大老爷要起兵出征，我丈\n夫要从征出战。为此奴家，备了些酒肴在此，与他饯行。怎么这般时候，还不\n见回来？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（花大汉上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "花大汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳。"
        },
        {
          "character": "花大汉",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为人莫当兵，做铁莫做钉。做钉被人打，当兵受苦情。"
        },
        {
          "character": "花大汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我，花大汉的便是。今早在辕门伺候，大老爷发令起兵，方才又传出令来，明\n早五鼓，就要起程。我想此番前去，不知胜败如何，生死难料。只得回来，与\n妻子分别一番。来此已是自己家门了。\n老婆开门来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是谁呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "花大汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是我。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "当家的回来啦，待我开门。\n哟，你回来啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "花大汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我回来了。咳，我当初为什么要当他娘的兵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我说当家的，大老爷几时起程呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "花大汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大老爷明日就要起程了。我是实实舍不得你，故此回来，与你分别。我的腰刀\n兵器，铺盖行李，可曾打点好了靡有？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "全给你预备好啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "花大汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你先拿我的铺盖来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "做什么呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "花大汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我先睡一会，到了五更天，就要开腿上路了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴家备得些酒肴在此，特与你饯饯行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "花大汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有酒？好，拿来咱们喝。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王氏送酒，斟。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一更鼓儿天，\n一更那鼓儿天。\n摆酒筵，就把行来饯。\n早回归，与奴重相见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "我儿夫征西摆着酒筵、好伤怀，望丈夫早回归、花大汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "干！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（打二更鼓。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二更鼓儿深，\n二更那鼓儿深。\n你须记妻子，我身怀孕。"
        },
        {
          "character": "你去不知，何日再相亲、花大汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你有了喜了么？我好伤心吓，也没个人来扶侍你，好苦呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴好伤心！\n奴好伤心！\n到了时，早寄阳关信。\n到了时，早寄一封阳关信。"
        },
        {
          "character": "去到边关万里长城、花大汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳！边关上，恐怕靡有人可以带信与你。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（打三更鼓。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三更鼓儿催，\n奴劝丈夫你多吃几杯！"
        },
        {
          "character": "三更那鼓儿催、花大汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我多喝几杯。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吃几杯，好与你同床睡。"
        },
        {
          "character": "花大汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳！我的骚娘呀，有什么心情，还想那话儿吗？一会儿就要拔腿上路了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴好凄惶！奴好凄惶！\n只有今宵，与你同床。\n你不眠，叫奴可如何样？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（花大汉倚桌睡。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "当家的睡吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（花大汉拔腰刀看。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "花大汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贼在哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我说是睡觉，哪儿有贼呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "花大汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "睡觉吓。呵呀，我的娘。明日上阵，要跑马射箭的，还干这个事吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（打四更鼓。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四更鼓儿沉，\n只有今宵一刻千金。\n你此去，不知在哪处儿困。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四更那鼓儿沉、出门人，不好多相问、花大汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪有什么好所在，不过是帐房里头罢了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一路小心！一路小心！\n你去后又有谁来问。\n你去后，谁来把你问。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（打五更鼓。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "五更鼓儿敲，\n奴对丈夫哭号啕。\n你且莫心焦，你且莫心焦。\n巴得的早回来，与你同欢笑。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（鸡叫。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "花大汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呵呀！不好了，天色明了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "花大汉",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天色明了，天色已明了，\n打点行李，挂在马鞍桥。\n我去后，你莫被旁人笑。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（老二上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "老二",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "旁人笑，旁人笑，大老爷已放了起身炮。我好笑。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "花大汉昨晚上回家，今日这时候还不见到，又得我来叫他。说着，说着，到了。\n老大，开门来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "花大汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪个小屄养的，天将亮就来打门！"
        },
        {
          "character": "老二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳，怎么就骂起来了。老大，是我。"
        },
        {
          "character": "花大汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我开门看，原来是老二吓，得罪，得罪，家里坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这是谁呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "花大汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这是你嫂子。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "婊子？待我来嫖嫖。"
        },
        {
          "character": "花大汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳！是你嫂子。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是嫂子。来见个礼儿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "花大汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不见罢了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嫂子我这儿有礼了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这是谁？"
        },
        {
          "character": "花大汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是你的二兄弟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老大，大老爷放了起身炮。头队二队，都开跋了，快些走罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叔叔，大老爷已经起身了吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "老二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走了好一会了。老大，快走罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呵呀，丈夫吓，你要早去早回，路上要保重！"
        },
        {
          "character": "花大汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老婆呀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "花大汉",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呵呀我的姣姣，我的姣姣。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不要挑啦，扛着走罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（老二拉花大汉。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "花大汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我出去打仗，难道说兵器也不叫人带么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "老二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "让你拿了家伙。快走！"
        },
        {
          "character": "花大汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兄弟，你叫我进去说一句话。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只许说一句。要是说两句，就是王八蛋日的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "花大汉",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我的姣姣，我的姣姣。\n行囊挂在马鞍桥。\n我去后，休被旁人笑。"
        },
        {
          "character": "我去后，休被旁人笑、老二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走罢，走罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（老二拉花大汉同下，老二上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "老二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我说这个嫂子。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叔叔为何去了又转来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "老二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个……那个……嫂子，我在这与你见个礼儿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "方才见过了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嫂子，老大此番前去，只怕回不来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为何出此不利之言？"
        },
        {
          "character": "老二",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他若是回不来，我就同嫂子，那个……"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀啐！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王氏打老二，老二下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "冤家你去了，\n撇得奴家冷悄悄。\n怎生煞，倒不如，抱琵琶去弹别调。\n养下儿，叫谁人抱。"
        },
